reviews.snippet:
Tempat nongkrong dengan pilihan berbagai macam makanan dan cemilan, cocok utk bersantai, harga dari yg murah sampai yg mahal, bisa milih sesuai selera

Disini aku jajan old changkee, jajanan ala singapore kyk gorengan sate-sate gitu, sama mesen minumannya es leci tea

A hangout spot with a wide selection of food and snacks, perfect for relaxing. Prices range from cheap to expensive, allowing you to choose according to your taste.

response.snippet: Terima kasih, Kak Paramitha, atas ulasannya! Kami senang mengetahui bahwa Kakak menikmati suasana dan hidangan Nasi Udang Telur Asin di Pancar Garden. Meskipun cuaca hujan, kami senang Kakak tetap menikmati pengalaman di sini. Sampai jumpa di kunjungan berikutnya!
response.translated_snippet: Thank you, Kak Paramitha, for your review! We are glad to know that you enjoyed the atmosphere and the Salted Egg Shrimp Rice dishes at Pancar Garden. Despite the rainy weather, we are glad that you still enjoyed your experience here. See you on your next visit!
